body_html: Thank you @ezyang! What I don't get is why the error is showing up on a build that does not involve libtorch, as libtorch is only built on pr/pytorch-linux-xenial-cuda9-cudnn7-py3 and pr/pytorch-linux-trusty-py3.6-gcc7.2. Could it be leftover CMakeCache.txt or the like?

body: Thank you @ezyang! What I don't get is why the error is showing up on a build that does not involve `libtorch`, as `libtorch` is only built on  `pr/pytorch-linux-xenial-cuda9-cudnn7-py3` and `pr/pytorch-linux-trusty-py3.6-gcc7.2`. Could it be leftover `CMakeCache.txt` or the like?
